Package domain.block

Class SequenceBlock

java.lang.Object
domain.block.Block
domain.block.SequenceBlock
Direct Known Subclasses:
ActionBlock, FunctionCallBlock, SurroundingBlock
public abstract class SequenceBlock
extends Block
An abstract class of SequenceBlocks that extends Block and has a next and previous block.
Version:
4.0
Author:
Andreas Awouters Thomas Van Erum Dirk Vanbeveren Geert Wesemael
